<p class="ql-align-center">丝路风情</p>
<p>丝绸之路，源远流长，审视石窟艺术，感到收获颇多。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190225/1af39c40ccc44827add7d5a1caab2da9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
