<p>丝绸之路，艺术采风，随意选取角度，画出心中所想。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190225/f8307b6ca9444d12abac81a4103223f2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
