<p class="ql-align-center">穿过沙漠遇见你</p>
<p>用心用笔记录了这一路上的风景。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190225/59fc6c8bb029408f92e8f286cd6c68af.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
