<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190225/854a57d926384ce2816d924151fa60a0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">敦煌之路</p>
<p>那个位于河西走廊最西端，被沙漠戈壁包围的古城敦煌以它所散发出的神秘感和艺术气息深深吸引着远在西安的我。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190225/cb3bd68bf17540eebd08f37f5058b91e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>现实生活丰富多采，瞬息万变，许多珍贵的瞬间是可一而不可再，可遇而不可求的。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190225/757313222064433892f72667dc83135a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
