<p>令人心驰神往的艺术采风。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190225/2297dde98b344153b5d2969f0afc5e70.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190225/49b1e7e51d85453b98eabdcd5477d98e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">采风速写</p>
<p>走在丝绸之路上，重温经典作品。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190225/6aa57481ebc84dddb3a8379107af3c9b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
